Denial of Death. This is the first book I got you.

1338
01:16:22,000 --> 01:16:24,080
噢，上帝，是的 - 还记得那天吗?
Remember that day?

1339
01:16:24,080 --> 01:16:27,160
天哪，我感到我背后的负担减轻了好多
I feel like there's a great weight off my back.

1340
01:16:28,160 --> 01:16:28,960
多谢了，亲爱的
Thanks, honey.

1341
01:16:28,960 --> 01:16:35,320
