My analyst thinks this move is key for me.

1344
01:16:42,520 --> 01:16:46,720
是啊，你知道，我相信她 因为她是我的心理医生推荐的
And I trust her, because my analyst recommended her.

1345
01:16:46,800 --> 01:16:49,760
